  "authors": [],
  "body": {
    "comment": "I vote YES on the treasury withdrawal action “Intersect Technical Steering Committee Support” (b3d452bff7769d7f557ec6b8974760ee6c5e496c276652b654032966621e0ccf#3).\n\nThe Technical Steering Committee of Intersect also supports the Parameter Committee, Hard Fork Working Group and Security Council. All elements that have played a pivotal role in Cardano’s growth and resilience over this past year. Including Plutus Cost Model, tx and memory unit, and committeeMinSize parameter updates, the van Rossem hard fork coordination, chain partition incident response and SecondFi assistance.\n\nIt’s not necessarily work that makes headlines but it does help keep Cardano secure and operational, reducing any negative headlines."
  },
  "hashAlgorithm": "blake2b-256"
}
